bilingual.source: An article used to outfit or equip.
bilingual.target: 装备，家具，服装用来装备或配备的物品。
他已经准备好了露营装备。
阿什利：我来了！找到一个装备。

bilingual.source: I'll have your outfit ready in five minutes.
bilingual.target: 我会在五分钟的装备准备好。
他的电脑系统暨装备是低劣的。

bilingual.source: Prepare an emergency outfit in your closet.
bilingual.target: 在你的储藏室里准备紧急装备。

bilingual.source: He got a fly - ass ninJa outfit and parachute.
bilingual.target: 他有忍者飞行的全套装备和降落伞.
玛利亚·莎拉波娃的全套网球装备：180,000日元

bilingual.source: It was this ruffle outfit and I couldn't get out of it!
bilingual.target: 这是这个生气装备和我无法摆脱它！

yingyinNormal.en: That's Alicia May Emory's outfit!
yingyinNormal.zh: 啊，这是Alicia May Emory的装备！

yingyinNormal.en: They have it. They have the Mockingjay outfit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们已经做出来了，他们做出了嘲笑鸟的服装。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Hey. Didn't you have that outfit on last night?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是昨晚那套衣服。

yingyinNormal.en: And Emma needs a cowgirl outfit for the competition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 爱玛得穿牛仔装！

yingyinNormal.en: No, I'm just here to buy a kid an outfit. I know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我只是来这给孩子买件衣服。我知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Where am I gonna get a cowgirl outfit on Thanks Giving?
yingyinNormal.zh: 感恩节我上哪儿找牛仔装啊？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm coming to see you. I'm going to wear my nurse's outfit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来看你吧，我要穿我的护士装啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait a second. Where have I seen that cowgirl outfit before?
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，我好像在什么地方见过这身牛仔...

yingyinNormal.en: Are you gonna put on that cheerleader outfit again? No. You wish.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你又要穿啦啦队服了吗？不是，你希望吧，不是。

yingyinNormal.en: My favorite outfit was the glittery boots and my bumblebee tights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最喜欢的搭配就是我的闪闪雨鞋和大黄蜂连裤袜。

yingyinNormal.en: Points for funny. Oh, was it the weird outfit? Because there's a reason.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为你的幽默加分。是因为那套奇怪的战服吗？那事出有因。

yingyinNormal.en: Nikki, stop. There are five things wrong with Nikki's outfit. What are they?
yingyinNormal.zh: 妮基，站住，妮基的服饰有5处明显的不当，请问分别是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Riley, just because I'm wearing an outfit similar to yours doesn't make me you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱丽，仅仅因为我穿了一件和你的相似的外套，并不会让我变成你。

yingyinNormal.en: He went AWOL after Calantha with a few more in his outfit I wouldn't mind closing out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡兰塔殖民战役后他就离开了军队，当了逃兵，他所带的小队中还有几个在逃，真恨不得早点了结他们。

yingyinNormal.en: No. Wait, you know what, this is the outfit that makes my calves look fat. Never mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有，等等，这件衣服会显得我小腿很粗，算了。

yingyinNormal.en: He practically begged me to come and look at your outfit here. Called in a personal favor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他让我来这里看看你到底有些什么，为了让我帮他这个忙，他打电话的时候都差不多是在求我了

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, I picked up this outfit that I want to wear, and the boots don't really go with it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经挑好了我要穿的衣服，靴子跟它不配。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Okay. How can I help you? Well, do you have a Santa outfit left? Two days before Christmas? Sorry, man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，需要什么？还有没有圣诞老人的衣服？圣诞节前两天？ 抱歉。

yingyinNormal.en: Samaritan has uncovered evidence that an ISA agent allowed members of a criminal outfit to escape with our virus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 撒马利亚人发现一位ISA特工放走了犯罪组织的成员，让他们带病毒逃了。

yingyinNormal.en: I put on a cheer-leading outfit to seduce Joshua. Then I lost him because I asked him to marry me after four dates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我打扮得像个啦啦队长，倒追约书亚，约了四次会就叫他娶我，把他吓死了。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: a set of clothes worn together, typically for a particular occasion or purpose

examination_example.sentence: But no one can be unique with their <highlight>outfit</highlight> every day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是没有人可以每天都穿独一无二的衣服。
她觉得她的服装不合适。

examination_example.sentence: What overwhelms the speaker when she buys her summer <highlight>outfits</highlight> each year?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 述者每年购买夏季装备时，是什么使她不知所措？

examination_example.sentence: Ease of care was most important; summer dresses and <highlight>outfits</highlight>, in particular, were chiefly cotton, readily capable of being washed and pressed at home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 易于护理是最重要的; 特别是夏天的裙子和套装都主要是棉布制成的，很容易在家里洗和熨。
